26 “(b) Improve equity in behavioral health treatment and ensure culturally,
27 linguistically and developmentally appropriate responses to individuals ex-
28 periencing behavioral health crises, in recognition that, historically, crisis
29 response services placed marginalized communities at disproportionate risk
30 of poor outcomes and criminal justice involvement;
HB 4070-9 2/11/26
